{"type": "article", "id": 9828, "title": "“Tableau” 自动灌溉系统", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-21T07:08:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135810Uhnb62ul4fAz7kTO.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t来自荷兰的设计工作室 Pikaplant 最近推出了一个叫做 “Tableau” 的自动灌溉系统，这个系统包括三个陶瓷花盆，一个连接到蓄水盆的金属基底，模仿植物的自然循环，能够自动给植物浇水。设计简单干净，几乎适合摆放在家里任何位置。目前售价 125 欧元，正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/pikaplant/tableau-automatic-house-plant-watering-tray\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135806IAaZkfVSCqTb3iRO.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061358069jaV14Bv2A0FyTSr.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135806q8JlDy7EbpRoOVHt.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135807qpgJUOiKzarHZwMo.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135808YkphTra1xzFSR5nj.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135809ef1Hd3cwiBAv9GK8.gif\" alt=\"\" s